{"lemma":"صُمُّ","slug":"صُمُّ","root":"ص.م.م","root_slug":"ص-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-م-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"أَصَمّ","root":"صمم","pos":"N","occurrence_count":12},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n24840"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"deaf"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause or render deaf, to deafen","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lose one's hearing, to become deaf","tags":["intransitive"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Color or defect adjective from the root ص م م (ṣ m m)."},"ipa":["/ʔa.sˤamm/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n24840","headword_ar":"صّمَّ","root":"Sm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Samima","text_ar":"صَمِمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is extr., (M, K,) [first pers. of each"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Samimotu","text_ar":"صَمِمْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaSam~u","text_ar":"يَصَمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamamN","text_ar":"صَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~N","text_ar":"صَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSam~a","text_ar":"اَصَمَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, deaf;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, * Msb, K; *) [or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a stoppage of the ear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a heaviness of hearing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~ati AlA^u*unu","text_ar":"صَمَّتِ الاُذُنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamamN","text_ar":"صَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ear was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, deaf."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  [And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, as though he heard not."},{"kind":"text","text":"] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a Eanohu","text_ar":"صَمَّ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was as though he heard not him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it; he was deaf to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (M;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanohu","text_ar":"عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSam~a","text_ar":"اَصَمَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the same]. (S, M.) ―         -b3-  [Hence"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a","text_ar":"صَمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, uttered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made, no sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"noise;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like him who, not hearing, returns no reply to a call or question; (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was dumb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mute."},{"kind":"text","text":"] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~ato HaSaApN bidamK","text_ar":"صَمَّتْ حَصَاةٌ بِدَمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A pebble made no sound"},{"kind":"text","text":"in falling upon the ground"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of blood"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e. the blood was so copious that if one threw a pebble into it no sound would be heard in consequence thereof, (As, S, M, Meyd, K, TA,) because it would not fall upon the ground: (As, S, Meyd:) the saying is a prov. (Meyd.) And hence the saying of Imra-el-Keys,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sm~iY A@bonapa Aljabali","text_ar":"صمِّى ا@بْنَةَ الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) in the following verse:"},{"kind":"quote","text":"bud~ilotu mino waAy^ilK wakinodapa Eado\n                      \n                     \n                        waAna wafahomFA Sam~iY A@bonapa Aljabali"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have been given in exchange, for Wáïl and Kindeh,' Adwán and Fahm: make no sound, O pebble:"},{"kind":"text","text":"app. meaning that he would shed much blood]: (S, TA: but this verse is omitted in one of my two copies of the S:) or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O echo;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Meyd, K;) so they assert: (AHeyth, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O calamity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the saying being a prov.; (Meyd, TA;) applied to the case of a severe calamity; as though meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be dumb, O calamity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"said by As to be applied in relation to an event deemed excessively foul or evil: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O serpent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd, TA;) which is said to be the primary meaning: (Meyd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O rock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A Heyth, K, TA. [See also the second of the sentences here following.]) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a SadaAhu","text_ar":"صَمَّ صَدَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His echo became dumb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may his echo become dumb;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he perished,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may he perish."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~iY SamaAmi","text_ar":"صَمِّى صَمَامِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK erroneously written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sum~iY","text_ar":"صُمِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Increase, O calamity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA:) or it is applied to a man who brings to pass a calamity, and means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"be dumb, O calamity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamaAmi","text_ar":"صَمَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"war;"},{"kind":"text","text":"but primarily,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the serpent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and this saying, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~iY A@bonapa Aljabali","text_ar":"صَمِّى ا@بْنَةَ الجَبَلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", is a prov. said when two parties refuse to make peace, and persist in opposition; meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"answer not the charmer, O serpent, but continue as thou art wont to be."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Meyd.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamamN","text_ar":"صَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in relation to stones, (Lth, TA,) or stone, (M,) [app. as an inf. n.,] signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being hard"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and solid"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSam~u","text_ar":"اَصَمُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")]; or [as a simple subst.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hardness"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and solidity"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Lth, M, TA:) and in relation to a spear-shaft, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being compact;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compactness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a","text_ar":"صَمَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHajaru","text_ar":"الحَجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamamN","text_ar":"صَمَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The stone was hard"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and solid"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (MA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~ati Alfitonapu","text_ar":"صَمَّتِ الفِتْنَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The trial,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"civil war,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, hard, vehement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"severe."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a AlqaAruwrapa","text_ar":"صَمَّ القَارُورَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~N raA^osa AlqaAruwrapi","text_ar":"صَمٌّ رَاْسَ القَارُورَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (PS, [in a copy of the M"},{"kind":"text","text":", contr. to a general rule in the case of a trans. verb of this class, and app. a mistranscription,]) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~N","text_ar":"صَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stopped the flask"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottle"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SamaAm","text_ar":"صَمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1723},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stopped the head of the flask"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bound it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASm~hu","text_ar":"اصمّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASm~ AlqaAruwrapa","text_ar":"اصمّ القَارُورَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SimaAm","text_ar":"صِمَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the flask"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bottle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~a AljuroHa","text_ar":"صَمَّ الجُرْحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~N","text_ar":"صَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound the wound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put upon it a bandage with medicament."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~ahu","text_ar":"صَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sam~N","text_ar":"صَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He struck him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. his head, (M,) with a staff, or stick, (S, M,) and with a stone, (S, M, K,) and with the like thereof. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sum~a","text_ar":"صُمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was struck vehemently."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","As","Meyd","TA","AHeyth","Lth"]}]}}